OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry first thing with sunny
OL,6,Fspells. Thickening cloud and outbreaks
OL,7,Fof light rain will spread north into
OL,8,FOrkney through the morning, then into
OL,9,FShetland in the afternoon. Patchy low
OL,10,Fcloud and haar in places.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRain and low cloud clear
OL,13,FShetland through the evening, dry with
OL,14,Fclear spells over Orkney. Another
OL,15,Fspell of rain spreads north overnight.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FOvernight rain clearing away
OL,18,Fin the morning with some haar at first
OL,19,Facross Shetland. Then mainly dry with
OL,20,Fsome hazy sunshine and just the odd
OL,21,Fshower possible. A bit warmer.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
