OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FOften
OL,6,Fdry and with bright spells and
OL,7,Fvariable cloud through the weekend and
OL,8,Fbut cloudier with some rain possible
OL,9,Fearly Sunday. A touch cooler, cloudier
OL,10,FMonday with rain at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
